name: Commonwealth of Pennsylvania, Appellant, v. George Shollenberger

parties: Commonwealth of Pennsylvania, Appellant, v. George Shollenberger.

opinions.text:
Per Curiam,
The judgment of this Court heretofore entered (170 Pa. 296) having been reversed by the Supreme Court of the United States, it is now ordered that the judgment of the court of quarter sessions of Philadelphia county be and the same is hereby affirmed with costs.
opinions.author: Per Curiam,

casebody.head_matter:
Commonwealth of Pennsylvania, Appellant, v. George Shollenberger.
No. 104, July T., 1894. Appeal from Q. S. Phila. Co.
